<div class="chapter" id="ch3">
  <div class="chapter-header">
    <div class="chapter-num">Chapter 03</div>
    <h2>積分</h2>
    <p>リーマン積分の定義から始まり、置換積分・部分積分の証明、面積・体積・弧長計算、広義積分まで丁寧に扱う。</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 3.1 不定積分・定積分 -->

  <div class="section" id="int-def">
    <h3>3.1 不定積分と定積分</h3>

```
<div class="formula-box definition">
  <strong>不定積分：</strong>$F'(x)=f(x)$ のとき $\displaystyle\int f(x)\,dx = F(x)+C$
</div>

<div class="formula-box definition">
  <strong>定積分（リーマン積分）：</strong>
  $$\int_a^b f(x)\,dx = \lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{k=1}^n f\!\left(a+\frac{b-a}{n}k\right)\cdot\frac{b-a}{n}$$
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
  <strong>微積分学の基本定理：</strong>
  $$\frac{d}{dx}\int_a^x f(t)\,dt = f(x)$$
  $$\int_a^b f(x)\,dx = F(b) - F(a) \quad (F'=f)$$
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>基本定理の証明：</strong> $G(x)=\displaystyle\int_a^x f(t)\,dt$ とおく。
  $$G(x+h)-G(x) = \int_x^{x+h}f(t)\,dt$$
  $f$ が連続なので積分の平均値定理より $\exists \xi \in [x,x+h]$ s.t. $\displaystyle\int_x^{x+h}f(t)\,dt = f(\xi)\cdot h$
  $$\frac{G(x+h)-G(x)}{h} = f(\xi) \to f(x)\ (h\to 0,\ \xi\to x)$$
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<h4>基本積分公式</h4>
<table>
  <tr><th>$f(x)$</th><th>$\int f(x)\,dx$</th></tr>
  <tr><td>$x^n\ (n\neq-1)$</td><td>$\dfrac{x^{n+1}}{n+1}+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$\dfrac{1}{x}$</td><td>$\log|x|+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$e^x$</td><td>$e^x+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$a^x$</td><td>$\dfrac{a^x}{\log a}+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$\sin x$</td><td>$-\cos x+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$\cos x$</td><td>$\sin x+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$\dfrac{1}{\cos^2 x}$</td><td>$\tan x+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}$</td><td>$\arcsin x+C$</td></tr>
  <tr><td>$\dfrac{1}{1+x^2}$</td><td>$\arctan x+C$</td></tr>
</table>
```

  </div>

  <!-- 3.2 積分技法 -->

  <div class="section" id="int-technique">
    <h3>3.2 積分技法</h3>

```
<h4>置換積分法</h4>
<div class="formula-box theorem">
  $x = g(t)$ とおくと（$g$ は微分可能かつ単射）：
  $$\int f(x)\,dx = \int f(g(t))g'(t)\,dt$$
  定積分では：$\displaystyle\int_a^b f(x)\,dx = \int_\alpha^\beta f(g(t))g'(t)\,dt$（$g(\alpha)=a$，$g(\beta)=b$）
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>証明：</strong>$F'=f$ として $H(t)=F(g(t))$ を微分すると連鎖律より $H'(t)=f(g(t))g'(t)$，よって $\int f(g(t))g'(t)\,dt = F(g(t))+C = F(x)+C = \int f(x)\,dx$
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<h4>部分積分法</h4>
<div class="formula-box theorem">
  $$\int f(x)g'(x)\,dx = f(x)g(x) - \int f'(x)g(x)\,dx$$
  $$\int_a^b f(x)g'(x)\,dx = \Bigl[f(x)g(x)\Bigr]_a^b - \int_a^b f'(x)g(x)\,dx$$
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>証明：</strong>積の微分 $(fg)' = f'g+fg'$ を積分：$\displaystyle\int (fg)'\,dx = \int f'g\,dx + \int fg'\,dx$
  $$f(x)g(x) = \int f'g\,dx + \int fg'\,dx \implies \int fg'\,dx = fg - \int f'g\,dx$$
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
  <strong>例題 3.2.1：</strong> $\displaystyle\int x e^x\,dx$ を求めよ。<br>
  <div class="answer-block">
    $f=x$，$g'=e^x$ として部分積分：$xe^x - \displaystyle\int e^x\,dx = xe^x - e^x + C = (x-1)e^x+C$
  </div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
  <strong>例題 3.2.2：</strong> $I = \displaystyle\int e^x\sin x\,dx$ を求めよ。<br>
  <div class="answer-block">
    $I = e^x\sin x - \displaystyle\int e^x\cos x\,dx = e^x\sin x - \left[e^x\cos x - \int e^x(-\sin x)\,dx\right]$<br>
    $= e^x\sin x - e^x\cos x - I$<br>
    $2I = e^x(\sin x-\cos x)$ より $I = \dfrac{e^x(\sin x-\cos x)}{2}+C$
  </div>
</div>

<h4>有理関数の積分（部分分数分解）</h4>

<div class="example-box">
  <strong>例題 3.2.3：</strong> $\displaystyle\int\frac{1}{x^2-1}\,dx$ を求めよ。<br>
  <div class="answer-block">
    $\dfrac{1}{x^2-1}=\dfrac{1}{(x-1)(x+1)}=\dfrac{1/2}{x-1}-\dfrac{1/2}{x+1}$<br>
    $= \dfrac{1}{2}\log|x-1| - \dfrac{1}{2}\log|x+1| + C = \dfrac{1}{2}\log\left|\dfrac{x-1}{x+1}\right|+C$
  </div>
</div>

<h4>三角関数の積分</h4>
<div class="formula-box">
  $$\int \sin^2 x\,dx = \frac{x}{2}-\frac{\sin 2x}{4}+C,\quad \int \cos^2 x\,dx = \frac{x}{2}+\frac{\sin 2x}{4}+C$$
  $$\int\frac{dx}{\sin x} = \log\left|\tan\frac{x}{2}\right|+C,\quad \int\frac{dx}{\cos x} = \log\left|\tan\left(\frac{x}{2}+\frac{\pi}{4}\right)\right|+C$$
</div>

<h4>ワリスの公式（重要）</h4>
<div class="formula-box theorem">
  $I_n = \displaystyle\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^n x\,dx$ について：
  $$I_n = \begin{cases} \dfrac{(n-1)!!}{n!!}\cdot\dfrac{\pi}{2} & n \text{ が偶数} \\ \dfrac{(n-1)!!}{n!!} & n \text{ が奇数} \end{cases}$$
  ここで $n!! = n(n-2)(n-4)\cdots$（二重階乗）。
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>漸化式の導出：</strong>部分積分で：
  $$I_n = \int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^{n-1}x\cdot\sin x\,dx = \Bigl[-\sin^{n-1}x\cos x\Bigr]_0^{\pi/2}+(n-1)\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^{n-2}x\cos^2 x\,dx$$
  $= (n-1)\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^{n-2}x(1-\sin^2 x)\,dx = (n-1)(I_{n-2}-I_n)$<br>
  $$\therefore I_n = \frac{n-1}{n}I_{n-2}$$
  $I_0=\pi/2$，$I_1=1$ から計算できる。
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>
```

  </div>

  <!-- 3.3 積分の応用 -->

  <div class="section" id="int-apply">
    <h3>3.3 積分の応用</h3>

```
<h4>面積</h4>
<div class="formula-box">
  $$S = \int_a^b |f(x)-g(x)|\,dx$$
</div>

<h4>回転体の体積</h4>
<div class="formula-box">
  <strong>$x$ 軸回転：</strong>$V = \pi\displaystyle\int_a^b \{f(x)\}^2\,dx$<br><br>
  <strong>$y$ 軸回転（バウムクーヘン分割）：</strong>$V = 2\pi\displaystyle\int_a^b x|f(x)|\,dx$
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>バウムクーヘン分割の導出：</strong><br>
  $x$ から $x+dx$ の薄い円筒（半径 $x$，高さ $f(x)$，厚み $dx$）の体積：$dV = 2\pi x f(x)\,dx$<br>
  積分して $V = 2\pi\displaystyle\int_a^b x f(x)\,dx$
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<h4>曲線の弧長</h4>
<div class="formula-box">
  $$L = \int_a^b \sqrt{1+\{f'(x)\}^2}\,dx$$
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>導出：</strong>微小弧 $ds$ は $ds = \sqrt{(dx)^2+(dy)^2} = \sqrt{1+\left(\dfrac{dy}{dx}\right)^2}dx$ なので積分。
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
  <strong>例題 3.3.1：</strong> $y=\dfrac{x^2}{2}-\dfrac{\log x}{4}$（$1\leq x\leq 2$）の弧長を求めよ。<br>
  <div class="answer-block">
    $y'=x-\dfrac{1}{4x}$，$1+(y')^2=\left(x+\dfrac{1}{4x}\right)^2$<br>
    $L = \displaystyle\int_1^2\left(x+\frac{1}{4x}\right)dx = \left[\frac{x^2}{2}+\frac{\log x}{4}\right]_1^2 = \frac{3}{2}+\frac{\log 2}{4}$
  </div>
</div>

<h4>広義積分</h4>
<div class="formula-box definition">
  $$\int_a^\infty f(x)\,dx = \lim_{R\to\infty}\int_a^R f(x)\,dx,\quad \int_a^b f(x)\,dx = \lim_{\varepsilon\to 0^+}\int_{a+\varepsilon}^b f(x)\,dx\ \text{（$x=a$ に特異点）}$$
</div>

<div class="example-box">
  <strong>例題 3.3.2：</strong> $\displaystyle\int_0^\infty e^{-x}\,dx$，$\displaystyle\int_0^1\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}}\,dx$ を求めよ。<br>
  <div class="answer-block">
    $\displaystyle\int_0^\infty e^{-x}\,dx = \lim_{R\to\infty}[-e^{-x}]_0^R = 1$<br>
    $\displaystyle\int_0^1\frac{dx}{\sqrt{x}} = \lim_{\varepsilon\to 0^+}[2\sqrt{x}]_\varepsilon^1 = 2$
  </div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
  <strong>ガウス積分（重要）：</strong>
  $$\int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{-x^2}\,dx = \sqrt{\pi}$$
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
  <strong>証明（極座標変換）：</strong> $I = \displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{-x^2}\,dx$ とおくと：
  $$I^2 = \int_{-\infty}^\infty\int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{-(x^2+y^2)}\,dx\,dy$$
  $x=r\cos\theta$，$y=r\sin\theta$（$r\geq 0$，$0\leq\theta<2\pi$）：
  $$I^2 = \int_0^{2\pi}\int_0^\infty e^{-r^2}\cdot r\,dr\,d\theta = 2\pi\cdot\left[-\frac{e^{-r^2}}{2}\right]_0^\infty = 2\pi\cdot\frac{1}{2}=\pi$$
  $I>0$ より $I=\sqrt{\pi}$。
  <div class="qed">■</div>
</div>
```

  </div>

  <!-- 練習問題 -->

  <div class="section" id="int-exercise">
    <h3>3.4 練習問題</h3>

```
<div class="exercise-block">
  <strong>(1)</strong> $\displaystyle\int\frac{x}{\sqrt{x^2+1}}\,dx$ を求めよ。
  <div class="answer-block">
    $u=x^2+1$ と置換：$\frac{1}{2}\displaystyle\int u^{-1/2}\,du = \sqrt{x^2+1}+C$
  </div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
  <strong>(2)</strong> $\displaystyle\int_0^1 x^2 e^x\,dx$ を求めよ。
  <div class="answer-block">
    部分積分2回：$[x^2 e^x]_0^1 - 2\int_0^1 xe^x\,dx = e - 2([xe^x]_0^1 - \int_0^1 e^x\,dx) = e-2(e-e+1)=e-2$
  </div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
  <strong>(3)</strong> $y=\sqrt{x}$，$y=x^2$ で囲まれた面積を求めよ。
  <div class="answer-block">
    交点：$x=0,1$。$\sqrt{x}\geq x^2$（$0\leq x\leq 1$）なので：<br>
    $S=\displaystyle\int_0^1(\sqrt{x}-x^2)\,dx=\left[\frac{2}{3}x^{3/2}-\frac{x^3}{3}\right]_0^1=\frac{2}{3}-\frac{1}{3}=\frac{1}{3}$
  </div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
  <strong>(4)</strong> $y=\sin x$（$0\leq x\leq\pi$）の $x$ 軸回転体の体積を求めよ。
  <div class="answer-block">
    $V=\pi\displaystyle\int_0^\pi\sin^2 x\,dx=\pi\int_0^\pi\frac{1-\cos 2x}{2}\,dx=\pi\left[\frac{x}{2}-\frac{\sin 2x}{4}\right]_0^\pi=\frac{\pi^2}{2}$
  </div>
</div>
```

  </div>
</div>

